---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Bizvents | Specialized Debt Recovery Agency">
	
	<nav class="hidden md:block fixed w-full z-50 bg-slate-900/95 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-slate-800 text-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center h-20">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center">
                    <a href="#" class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-wider text-white uppercase">
                        Bizvents
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="space-x-8"> <a href="#about" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors text-sm font-medium">About Us</a>
                    <a href="#mission" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors text-sm font-medium">Mission</a>
                    <a href="#services" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors text-sm font-medium">Services</a>
                    <a href="#vision" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors text-sm font-medium">Vision</a>
                    <a href="#contact" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors">Contact</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="relative bg-slate-900 min-h-[50vh] py-16 flex items-center justify-center text-center px-4 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-950 via-blue-800 to-blue-950 opacity-90 animate-gradient-bg"></div>     
           		
		<div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">
            Ethical & Structured <br/>
                <span class="text-blue-200">Debt Recovery Solutions</span>
            </h1>
			<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-blue-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				Part of Sterling Security. Trusted by financial institutions across India since 1999.
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
				<a href="#about" class="px-8 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white rounded-md font-semibold transition-all shadow-lg">
					Discover Bizvents
				</a>
				<a href="#contact" class="px-8 py-3 border border-blue-400 hover:bg-blue-500 hover:text-white text-blue-200 rounded-md font-semibold transition-all shadow-lg">
					Contact Us
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white scroll-mt-20">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-blue-900 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Who We Are</h2>
					<h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">About Us</h3>
					
					<div class="prose text-slate-600 space-y-4 text-justify leading-relaxed">
						<p>
							Bizvents is a specialized debt recovery agency since 1999 and part of the business vertical of Sterling Security, a trusted provider of security and housekeeping services in India for the last 35 years. Leveraging decades of operational excellence and a reputation in service delivery, Bizvents was established to meet the growing demand for ethical, efficient, and structured debt recovery solutions across India.
						</p>
						<p>
							At the strategic helm of the company is <strong>Wing Commander Raj Krishna (Retd.)</strong>, Chairman of Bizvents. A distinguished Air Force veteran with over 35 years of industry and leadership experience, he has played a pivotal role in shaping the company’s vision, systems, and long-term direction. While not involved in day-to-day operations, his guidance continues to influence Bizvents’ discipline, integrity, and commitment to high standards.
						</p>
						<p>
							The company’s operations are led by <strong>Mr. Harish Krishna</strong>, Chief executive, a graduate of Delhi University and an MBA in Marketing and HRD. With more than 26 years of experience in the banking and finance sector, he brings deep industry knowledge and hands-on managerial expertise to the organization. Personally involved in both the micro and macro functioning of the company, he ensures that every client receives individual attention, consistent communication, and reliable results.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="relative h-full min-h-[400px] bg-slate-100 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl border border-slate-200">
					<img src="/images/image-about.jpeg" alt="Meeting room" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="mission" class="py-20 bg-slate-900 text-white scroll-mt-20">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
			<h2 class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Core Values</h2>
			<h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Our Mission</h3>
			
			<p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
				Our mission at Bizvents is to ensure that the predefined targets of our clients are met through ethical, efficient, and structured debt recovery solutions in compliance with RBI guidelines.
			</p>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-left mt-12">
				<div class="bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 shadow-lg">
					<h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></span> Partner & Consultant
                    </h4>
					<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
						As both a debt recovery agency and a risk management consulting partner, our goal is to help financial institutions, Banks, and NBFC meet resolution on their targets, minimize defaults, and make informed decisions. We are committed to transparency, compliance, and professionalism in every interaction.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-lg border border-slate-700 shadow-lg">
					<h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></span> Service-Oriented
                    </h4>
					<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
						Driven by discipline and a service-oriented approach, Bizvents strives to deliver measurable results while maintaining respectful communication and upholding the highest standards of integrity.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="services" class="py-20 bg-slate-50 scroll-mt-20">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-blue-900 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">What We Do</h2>
				<h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Our Services</h3>
				<p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
					At Bizvents, we provide comprehensive service-oriented solutions for all banking and financial products. Our operations cover the full spectrum of recovery and risk-related services.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
				
				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow border-l-4 border-blue-600">
					<h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Telecalling Services</h4>
					<p class="text-slate-600">
						Early Warning calls, pre-delinquent follow-ups, flow collection calls, and recovery calls—designed to maintain payment discipline and reduce slippages at an early stage.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow border-l-4 border-blue-600">
					<h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Field Referrals</h4>
					<p class="text-slate-600">
						Both delinquent and non-delinquent accounts are serviced through trained field representatives who handle verifications, follow-ups, and on-site assessments with professionalism and tact.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow border-l-4 border-blue-600">
					<h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Field Collections</h4>
					<p class="text-slate-600">
						Direct field recovery for delinquent accounts and charged-off accounts, carried out with a disciplined, ethical, and process-driven approach to maximize resolution rates.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow border-l-4 border-blue-600">
					<h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Storage & Asset Handling</h4>
					<p class="text-slate-600">
						Secure storage and management of vehicles and durable goods collected during recovery operations, handled under strict supervision and compliance standards.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-12 bg-blue-100 border border-blue-200 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
				<p class="text-blue-900 font-medium">
					We operate with a complete infrastructure, supported by a network of trained professionals who ensure timely action, accurate reporting, and consistent results.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="vision" class="py-20 bg-white scroll-mt-20">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="lg:flex lg:items-center lg:gap-16">
				<div class="lg:w-1/2 mb-10 lg:mb-0">
					<img src="/images/image-company.jpeg" alt="Strategic planning" class="rounded-lg shadow-2xl" />
				</div>
				<div class="lg:w-1/2">
					<h2 class="text-blue-900 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Future & Integrity</h2>
					<h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Company Vision</h3>
					
					<div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 text-justify leading-relaxed">
						<p>
							At Bizvents, our vision is to deliver end-to-end recovery and risk management solutions that consistently meet our clients’ expectations. Achieving targets, maintaining quality, and ensuring complete client satisfaction are not just goals—they are the defining principles of our company.
						</p>
						<p>
							In a highly competitive financial landscape, Bizvents has built a strong reputation for its swift, dedicated, and effective response to client needs. Our ability to navigate complex scenarios with precision has allowed us to stand out and earn long-term trust.
						</p>
						<blockquote class="bg-slate-50 border-l-4 border-blue-900 p-4 italic text-slate-800 my-6">
							"Our leadership stands for human values, respect, and unwavering ethics... approaching difficult cases with empathy and strategic insight."
						</blockquote>
						<p>
							Our leadership is central to this success. At the head of the company stands an individual whose human values, respect, and unwavering ethics bring a unique balance to an otherwise aggressive industry. His exceptional ability to approach difficult cases with empathy and strategic insight enables him to resolve situations that others often cannot. This philosophy inspires our entire team and guides the way Bizvents works every day.
						</p>
						<p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 pt-2">
							Our vision is simple: to combine performance, integrity, and humanity—delivering strong, sustainable results while upholding the highest standards of professionalism.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-16 bg-blue-900 text-center">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
			<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Trusted by Industry Leaders</h3>
			<p class="text-blue-200 font-light uppercase tracking-widest">List of Clients available on request</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<footer id="contact" class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-300 py-16 border-t border-slate-900 scroll-mt-20">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
				
				<div>
					<h4 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-blue-900 pb-2 inline-block">Head Office</h4>
					<div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
						<p><span class="text-slate-500 block text-xs uppercase mb-1">Name of Proprietor</span> <strong class="text-white text-base">Mr Harish Krishna</strong></p>
						
						<p>
							<span class="text-slate-500 block text-xs uppercase mb-1">Mobile Number</span> 
							<a href="tel:9811771615" class="text-white text-base font-bold hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">
								9811771615
							</a>
						</p>

						<a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Bizvents,+FF+-8,9,10+PVR+shopping+complex,+Saket,+New+Delhi+110017" target="_blank" class="block mt-4 bg-slate-900/50 p-4 rounded border border-slate-800 hover:border-blue-500 transition-colors">
							<span class="text-blue-500 block text-xs uppercase font-bold mb-2">Address</span>
							<p class="leading-relaxed text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">
								FF -8,9,10 PVR shopping complex,<br>
								Above PVR Cinema, Saket,<br>
								New Delhi 110017
							</p>
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h4 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-blue-900 pb-2 inline-block">Infrastructures</h4>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
						<li class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-900 pb-2">
							<span class="text-slate-400">FOS Strength</span>
							<span class="text-white font-bold bg-blue-900/30 px-2 py-1 rounded">300+</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-900 pb-2">
							<span class="text-slate-400">No of PC’s</span>
							<span class="text-white font-bold">75</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-900 pb-2">
							<span class="text-slate-400">Telephone lines</span>
							<span class="text-white font-bold">90</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-900 pb-2">
							<span class="text-slate-400">Office Area</span>
							<span class="text-white font-bold">2500 sq ft</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-900 pb-2">
							<span class="text-slate-400">Telecallers</span>
							<span class="text-white font-bold">65</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h4 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider border-b border-blue-900 pb-2 inline-block">Branch Offices</h4>
					<div class="space-y-6 text-sm">
						
						<div class="group">
							<span class="text-blue-500 font-bold block mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Rajasthan</span>
							<a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=46+47+Ganesh+Vatika+Niwaru+road,+Jotwara,+Jaipur+302012" target="_blank" class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-slate-800 pl-3 hover:text-white block transition-colors">
								46 47 Ganesh Vatika near pani ke tanki vadh g ka chorha Niwaru road, Jotwara, Jaipur 302012
							</a>
						</div>
						
						<div class="group">
							<span class="text-blue-500 font-bold block mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Punjab - Haryana</span>
							<a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Shop+n+33+Modaran+complex,+Derabassi+district+Mohali,+Punjab+140507" target="_blank" class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-slate-800 pl-3 hover:text-white block transition-colors">
								Shop n° 33 Modaran complex near Domino’s Pizza, Derabassi district Mohali, Punjab 140507
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

			</div>
			
			<div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-slate-900 text-center text-xs text-slate-600 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
				<p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Bizvents. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p>Part of Sterling Security</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</footer>

</Layout>